{Speech 13}{}{He’s been ruling here ever since the Master was destroyed. He puts down anyone who disagrees\n with him… or they just "disappear." The place looks civilized on the top of things, but the truth is that it’s a killing ground for bloodthirsty mutants. There's a friend of a friend who had friends who disappeared after speaking up.}
