{Speech 13 Answer Exit*}{}{No, I’m not really interested.}
{Speech 14}{}{We all pretend that this is a civilized town, that we’re all on the up and up… but we all live\n in fear of the mutant rage. Each day, there are fewer and fewer humans.}
